18.text:
When I woke up, it was an unfamiliar place. 
 There is nothing you can remember other than your name. Apparently, amnesia ... 
 There was an Ashin girl Feste. It seems that he liked this by helping Goblin. 
 However, what about her "servant"? 
 The place I met Feste is "archeological sites just recently discovered." There may be clues to memory.

21.text:
Considering the future, it seems better to be an adventurer. 
 Pass the exam and complete the adventurer registration.

23.text:
Life as an adventurer has begun. 
 If you receive a request, meet people, and go around various lands, it will naturally find memories. 
 First of all, I would like to take on a good job that JAKE will introduce. 
 What kind of content is it?

24.text:
In Giant Dragon's Claw Marks, he encountered a legendary monster, Avalitia. In addition, a mysterious boy Merlofof, who flew from the sky, heard the word "visitors". 
 Are these related to the lost memory? 
 I would like to investigate in detail, but I don't ask Feste saying "I'm going to coin -tei." 
 Because Jake was blown out, "The host will give you a delegation."

25.text:
I was able to hear about the "visitors" from Bufferrier priest Walkin and his apprentice Milrene. 
 "Visitors" are Gentiles with special power. 
 It seems that the secret is in the Bahamar Highlands, Sacred Pillar of the Gods, the largest sacred place in Bufferrier.

26.text:
In "Sacred Pillar of the Gods", I met Aerines and Tyris, who came from the future 1000 years later. 
 They will release Avalitia and save this star from the future of destruction. 
 I decided to cooperate with it. 
 Immediately, there seems to be a request from Tyris.

27.text:
An abnormal reaction of the engram that appeared on the omnistron. 
 It is highly likely that it is an avalitaire. 
 Cooperate with AERINSE and succeed in releasing Avalitia.

28.text:
Request from coin -tei owner. 
 It seems to be a simple use, but the items to be delivered seem to be quite dangerous, "If you know the taste, you can't go back anymore."

29.text:
Feste, who had been talking to the stray cat mysteriously, suddenly said he would come to the "Horned Goat meat". 
 Let's follow this as a servant, without asking anything.

30.text:
A simple job that just sends a letter to the MinsterHorn priest. 
 But Jake's secrets that should not be touched were hidden.

31.text:
The coin -tei owner was assigned a job with the reason, "I should have asked another guy." 
 It seems better to be prepared for some danger.

32.text:
Tyris suddenly began listening to a stranger. 
 Did you get some serious information ...? 
 The expression was full of impatience and determination.

33.text:
Aerinse and Tyris are talking about something interesting. 
 You may be able to get a glimpse of the secret of the two mysterious people who came from the future.

34.text:
A rich man who has no nose has been talking about work. 
 He says he wants to donate an expensive, unusual and beautiful item that draws the interest of the oracle shrine maiden ...

82.text:
At the back of "Giant Dragon's Claw Marks", I was able to discover a strong monster and managed to defeat it. 
 According to Feste, this monster is a survivor of Avalitia, transcends space and time. 
 Why is there a monster that is considered to be an adventure monster? 
 And I have defeated it ... 

 Jake first went to Development Bureau, saying, "We must encourage the avalitaire." 
 And a boy came down from the sky. 
 The boy named Merloof left a mysterious tweet called "visitors." 
 Is it related to my memory? 
 Feste seems to be a memorable word, but you can't remember. 
 For now, return to Development Bureau and get a reward from Jake.

83.text:
